<h1>Welcome to Lunchparty Hub</h1>
<% count = Person.count %>
<p>There are currently <%= count.to_s + ' person'.pluralize(count) %> in queue.</p>
<br/>
<p>If you would like to join, click <%= link_to 'here', controller: 'queue', action: 'add' %>.</p>
<br/>
<p>If you're currently in the queue and need to drop out, click <%= link_to 'here', controller: 'queue', action: 'remove' %>.</p>